Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.83,0:23:07.09,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fad(500,500)}何も何も見つからない時も…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.11,0:23:11.23,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fad(500,500)}諦めずにあるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.44,0:23:18.17,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fad(500,500)}命燃やせ　今が全て
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.18,0:21:59.85,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}敞开心扉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.85,0:22:02.50,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}真实的痛感会迎来明天
